    <!-- Favourite Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="myFavouriteModal" role="dialog">
     <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
      <div class="modal-loader" ng-show="ShowLoader">
      </div>
      <div class="modal-content" ng-show="!ShowLoader">
       <div class="modal-body">
        <div class="row">
         <div class="modal-compare-list">
          <div class="col-sm-10 col-xs-10">
           <h3>
            My Favourites
           </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-2">
           <div aria-label="Close" class="close-favourite" data-dismiss="modal" ng-click="closeFav()">
           </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row gifDiv">
           <div class="gifloader">
           </div>
          </div>
          <div ng-class="Products.length &lt; 4 ? '' : 'favourite-list-slider ' ">
           <div class="col-sm-4 col-xs-12" ng-repeat="Product in Products">
            <a href="{{Product.Url}}" ng-click="registerEvent(Product, $event)" rel="nofollow">
             <div class="product-page-item">
              <div class="product-page-item-icons">
               <div class="field-tip custom-plus-tooltip">
                <div class="close-favourite" data-action="removeFavorite">
                </div>
                <span class="tip-content">
                 Remove from fav
                </span>
               </div>
              </div>
              <div class="product-page-item-image">
               <img alt="{{Product.Title}}" src="{{Product.MainImage}}"/>
              </div>
              <figcaption>
               <span>
                {{Product.Title}}
               </span>
               <div class="modal-compare-list-summary">
                <ul>
                 <li ng-repeat="Feat in Product.Features">
                  {{Feat.Item}}
                 </li>
                </ul>
               </div>
              </figcaption>
             </div>
            </a>
           </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-xs-12" ng-if="Products.length === 0">
           No Products Selected
          </div>
          <div class="row">
           <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div class="favourite-content">
             <p>
              The 'Favourites' feature lets you save products to view later. To remove a product from your favourites, simply select the 'X' button in the right-hand corner of the product image.
              <br/>
              <br/>
              Select 'Send Us an Enquiry' to fill out your details in the form and a member of the team will get in touch with you.
             </p>
             <div class="enquiry-button" ng-click="changeModals()">
              <div class="enquiry-button-content">
               <span>
                Send us an enquiry
               </span>
              </div>
             </div>
            </div>
           </div>
           <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div class="favourite-content">
             <p>
              Want to save these for later? Fill in an email address to send a list of your favourite products to yourself or to someone else.
             </p>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
        <div id="ctl00_FavoriteModal_viewBiz">
         <div id="ctl00_FavoriteModal_viewBiz_pM_pMP">
         </div>
         <div class="FormPanel" id="ctl00_FavoriteModal_viewBiz_pnlForm">
          <div class="row" ng-form="SendEmailForm">
           <div class="col-sm-6">
            <div class="form-group favorite-group">
             <div class="input-group">
              <input class="form-control" id="Email" name="Email" ng-model="Email" placeholder="Please enter your email..." required="" type="email"/>
              <span class="input-group-addon">
               *
              </span>
             </div>
            </div>
           </div>
           <div class="col-sm-6">
            <div class="form-group favorite-group">
             <button class="cta-blue" ng-click="sendFavoritesList(Email, $event)" ng-disabled="SendEmailForm.Email.$invalid">
              Send basket
             </button>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
          <input class="FormButton btn btn-primary" id="ctl00_FavoriteModal_viewBiz_btnOK" name="ctl00$FavoriteModal$viewBiz$btnOK" type="submit" value="Submit"/>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
